  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Erika Paskey LLC</strong> built the Munchin' Roulette app as a commercial app. This SERVICE is provided by Erika Paskey LLC and is intended for use as is.</p>

  <p>The app does not collect any personally identifiable information (PII), such as names, emails, or user accounts. Your location (ZIP code or GPS) is used solely to find nearby restaurants using the Yelp API. This data is not stored or shared.</p>

  <p>We do not store or track your activity. Any data retrieved through the Yelp API is subject to Yelp’s own privacy practices. We are not responsible for the accuracy of Yelp's data or your experiences at suggested businesses.</p>

  <p>If you choose to upgrade to the Pro version, your purchase will be processed through the app store’s payment system. No payment data is collected or stored by us.</p>

  <p>If you have questions or concerns, contact us at <strong>roulettembb@gmail.com</strong>.</p>

