  <h3>1. App Purpose</h3>
  <p>This app helps users randomly select a restaurant based on location and filters. It relies on Yelp data to provide restaurant listings and details.</p>

  <h3>2. No Guarantees</h3>
  <p>We do not guarantee the accuracy of restaurant listings, operating hours, or quality. Yelp data may be incomplete or inaccurate. We are not liable for any inconvenience, dissatisfaction, or harm resulting from a visit to a suggested restaurant.</p>

  <h3>3. Refund Policy</h3>
  <p>All purchases are final. Refunds are only provided if the app fails to function. Contact <strong>roulettembb@gmail.com</strong> for support.</p>

  <h3>4. No User Accounts</h3>
  <p>This app does not require account creation. We do not collect or store personal information such as names or emails.</p>

